1
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:09,800
Ashun.

2
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,360
Look at me, still alive and well,

3
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:11,880
standing right in front of you.

4
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,240
Don't you find it strange?

5
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:15,440
Everyone,

6
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:16,760
recently in the Lin Manor,

7
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,200
a series of bizarre murders has occurred.

8
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,000
They all stem from a

9
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,200
rare hallucinogen.

10
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,520
A hallucinogen?

11
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:22,760
What is that?

12
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,720
It is a kind of

13
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,880
spice that induces hallucinations.

14
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:30,760
Master Lin,

15
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,480
could you please tell us,

16
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:34,240
when you were in Madam Bai's room,

17
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,400
what exactly did you see?

18
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,920
At the time, I saw Bai Mei

19
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,240
right in front of me.

20
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:41,880
Yes.

21
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,280
Exactly.

22
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:44,960
Everyone,

23
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:46,800
this so-called hallucinogen

24
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,800
is simply inside this lamb oil lamp,

25
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:51,720
a toxic gas produced by adding ambergris.

26
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,120
Those who inhale the gas will hallucinate.

27
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,360
As for how it works,

28
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:57,840
it's just like how certain foods clash.

29
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:00,560
However,

30
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,440
we all use lamb oil lamps in the manor.

31
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:05,280
Why didn't we hallucinate?

32
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,600
That is because Ashun,

33
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,200
before preparing to kill,

34
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,120
would tamper with the lamb oil lamp

35
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,640
by adding the ambergris beforehand.

36
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,360
No wonder you asked me to tell everyone

37
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,120
to stay in their rooms alone tonight.

38
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,840
No matter what sounds they hear,

39
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,160
as long as they aren't summoned,

40
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,800
they shouldn't step out of their rooms.

41
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:11,920
So,

42
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,600
you set up a trap.

43
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:14,880
Smart.

44
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:16,480
But

45
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,920
you knew perfectly well

46
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,720
this Lamb Oil Lamp contains a hallucinogen.

47
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,160
Why

48
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,160
would you still take the risk?

49
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,320
Weren't you afraid

50
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,440
you'd hallucinate too?

51
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,920
We have Qingqing to thank for that.

52
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,240
She made an antidote for us in advance,

53
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,000
so we wouldn't be

54
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,800
affected by the hallucinogen in the Lamb Oil Lamp.

55
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:31,840
Ashun,

56
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,680
you must have the antidote for the hallucinogen too.

57
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,840
Who would have thought

58
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,880
this seemingly ordinary Lamb Oil Lamp

59
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,000
and ambergris

60
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,520
could cause such terrifying hallucinations?

61
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,640
Then how were you so sure

62
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,800
that Ashun was the killer?

63
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,560
Manager Lai told us, of course.

64
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,480
Laifu?

65
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:00,760
Everyone,

66
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,600
this fruit is called the Divine Fruit.

67
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,200
It originates from the Western Regions.

68
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,800
It clears the throat and nourishes the lungs.

69
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,640
Even if you've lost your voice,

70
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,880
just keeping one in your mouth

71
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,600
will restore it completely,

72
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,120
or even make it better than before.

73
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:15,640
Master Lin,

74
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,560
you should know who in this manor

75
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:18,840
would consume this, right?

76
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:20,600
Besides,

77
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,560
have you forgotten Ashun's background?

78
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,120
Chunxing,

79
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,760
do you know what this is?

80
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,160
This...

81
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,600
Isn't this the Divine Fruit

82
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,560
Madam Bai used to eat often?

83
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,480
Back then,

84
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,880
she often asked Ashun

85
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,520
to fetch it from Hongfu Theater.

86
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,320
I was the one who washed them clean

87
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,600
before sending them to her room.

88
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,040
Ashun?

89
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,720
Wasn't he the servant

90
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,840
exclusively serving Old Madam?

91
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:52,920
Why

92
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,560
would Madam Bai ask him to fetch it?

93
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,560
That's because Ashun

94
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,240
was Madam Bai's dowry servant.

95
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,720
After he followed Madam Bai into the manor,

96
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,800
Old Madam saw that he was mute

97
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:04,920
and honest,

98
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,400
so she took Ashun away

99
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,560
from Madam Bai.

100
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,360
I remember too.

101
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,560
Back then, Old Madam and the others said

102
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,080
Madam Bai was unfaithful

103
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,480
and couldn't bear children.

104
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,720
They often beat and scolded her.

105
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,640
Even the servants in the manor

106
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,880
ignored her.

107
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,400
Only Ashun

108
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,760
still helped her secretly.

109
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:29,840
Yes.

110
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,680
This is the fruit Bai Mei

111
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,760
loved to eat most when she was alive.

112
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,840
But after she died,

113
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,160
this kind of thing

114
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,280
never appeared in the manor again.

115
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,320
Inspector Huang,

116
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,400
didn't you say Laifu killed my mother?

117
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,600
What on earth is going on?

118
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,040
Laifu did steal the Lin family's property,

119
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,560
and he did have an affair with Judou.

120
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,960
But he didn't kill anyone.

121
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,640
The reason I said that

122
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,120
was just to deceive the public.

123
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,000
And then,

124
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,080
I deliberately took this out

125
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,320
to tell the killer

126
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,120
that I already have all the evidence,

127
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:06,640
luring him to come and silence us.

128
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:07,680
Then...

129
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,520
Then my mother and...

130
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,960
And... and Zifeng...

131
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:12,960
Of course, it was still him.

132
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,320
Have you forgotten

133
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,400
the power of the hallucinogen?

134
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,640
Why?

135
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,960
After Bai Mei died,

136
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,880
I never treated you poorly

137
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,720
just because Bai Mei brought you in.

138
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,680
Why did you...

139
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,080
Why did you do this?

140
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,320
Master Lin,

141
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,920
do you remember

142
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,360
after the Second Wife died,

143
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,880
we asked you

144
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,440
how many of these costumes

145
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:46,280
Madam Bai actually had?

146
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,000
Take a look at this one.

147
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:53,560
Yes.

148
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,320
This one is Bai Mei's.

149
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,000
Look here.

150
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,440
This is where she stabbed herself with a dagger.

151
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,400
I found a top-notch embroiderer

152
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:01,760
to mend it.

153
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,560
So unless you look closely,

154
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,320
you can't tell at all.

155
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,480
That makes sense.

156
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,400
We found that Zifeng

157
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,120
was wearing a costume when she died.

158
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,080
If this one is real,

159
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,640
then the one on Zifeng

160
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,800
that was burned

161
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:16,720
must be fake.

162
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,600
Who

163
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,560
would go to such great lengths

164
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,960
to find an identical costume

165
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,320
and put it on Zifeng?

166
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,880
Since you won't admit it,

167
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,720
then I have no choice

168
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,640
but to destroy this costume myself.

169
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:40,880
No!

170
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,440
You...

171
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,720
You finally spoke.

172
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:55,600
This is what you get for being so nosy.

173
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,440
You're not mute.

174
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,520
Ever since she died,

175
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,040
I realized

176
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,480
that I could still speak.

177
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:29,960
Bai

178
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,200
Mei

179
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,040
Sister

180
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,360
Bai

181
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,320
Mei

182
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,560
Sister

183
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:52,120
Bai

184
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,520
Mei

185
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,720
Sister

186
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,880
Just because of this,

187
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,360
you killed everyone in the Lin family?

188
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,080
Yes.

189
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,600
I killed them all.

190
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,240
Because they all deserve to die, darn it.

191
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,440
Sister Bai Mei,

192
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,320
she was originally

193
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,840
the kindest and purest person in this world.

194
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,520
Lin Guorong,

195
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,160
do you know

196
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:30,040
when she learned she could marry you,

197
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,240
how much she looked forward to it,

198
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,560
and how happy she was?

199
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,360
What's wrong?

200
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,960
Are you still worried

201
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,840
that my status as an actress isn't good enough for Guorong,

202
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:50,040
and afraid I'll be wronged marrying into the Lin family?

203
00:09:58,920 --> 00:09:59,680
Ashun,

204
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:00,960
don't worry.

205
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,480
I believe in Guorong's feelings for me.

206
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,000
He will definitely protect me in the Lin family.

207
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,400
Besides,

208
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,160
you will also accompany me when I marry him,

209
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:09,680
won't you?

210
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,200
Look,

211
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,240
tomorrow,

212
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,320
I will wear the costume from the day

213
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,600
I first met Guorong to get married.

214
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,000
He will definitely be very happy too.

215
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,320
She trusted you so much

216
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,160
and loved you.

217
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:41,560
But you,

218
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,800
and everyone in your Lin family,

219
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,320
how did you treat her?

220
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,920
Loved me?

221
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,040
She didn't love me at all!

222
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,560
In bed, in her sleep,

223
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,880
she was calling someone else's name!

224
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,360
Lin Guorong, you jerk!
